Package: PleistoDist
Title: Calculating Island Geomorphologies Over Pleistocene Time
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("David", "Tan", , "david.tanjx@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7019-7871"))
Description: Visualising and quantifying the effects of Pleistocene-era sea level change on islands over time. 
    This tool is used to generate maps of island extents for different Pleistocene-era sea levels and 
    calculate various inter-island and intra-island distance and geo-morphological metrics over time, as described in 
    Tan D, Gyllenhaal EF, Andersen MJ (2022) <doi:10.1101/2022.05.13.491891>. Vignettes for this package can be found 
    at <https://davidbirdtan.com/pleistodist/>.
